The candidate is expected to teach at the didactic and clinical levels in both undergraduate and graduate programs in Dental Anaesthesia at the Faculty of Dentistry, as well as supervise graduate student research. In addition, the candidate must demonstrate the ability to develop and direct the graduate specialty program in Dental Anaesthesia.

